50 A.3d 604 ATTORNEY GRIEVANCE COMMISSION OF MARYLAND, Petitioner v. Kenneth John MacFADYEN, Respondent. Misc. Docket AG No. 13,

Sept. Term, 2012.

Court of Appeals of Maryland. Aug. 20, 2012.

*604 ORDER

This Court having considered the Joint Petition for Reprimand by Consent filed herein pursuant to Maryland Rule 16-772, it is this 20th day of August, 2012,

ORDERED, by the Court of Appeals of Maryland, a majority of the Court concurring, that Kenneth John MacFadyen, Respondent, is hereby reprimanded for professional misconduct in violation of Rules 5.1(a), 5.3(a) and 8.4(a) & (d) of the Maryland Lawyers’ Rules of Professional Conduct.
